==English==
===Noun===
'''[[nought]]s and [[cross]]es''' {{UK}}

#A two-player game played on a three-by-three grid, in which players take it in turns to play their respective symbol (either a nought or a cross) in a cell of the grid, the objective being to form a row, column or diagonal of three of one's own symbol.

====Synonyms====
*[[ticktacktoe]] ''or'' [[tic-tac-toe]] {{US}}

